# DevOps Assignment

This project implements a **production-oriented infrastructure setup** for a FastAPI backend and a Next.js frontend application.

While the application itself is intentionally simple, the primary focus of this repository is **DevOps infrastructure design, containerization, CI/CD automation, and deployment on AWS using Infrastructure as Code (Terraform).**

---

