# Deployment Infrastructure

The project uses **AWS EC2 and Docker-based deployment**.

Infrastructure components include:

- Terraform EC2 instance (Infrastructure provisioning)
- Jenkins EC2 instance (CI/CD automation)
- Dockerized frontend and backend services
- Docker Compose deployment strategy

---

# CI/CD Pipeline (Jenkins)

Pipeline workflow:

1. Pull latest code from GitHub fork
2. Build Docker images
3. Deploy containers using Docker Compose
4. Restart containers when new builds are triggered

